        "**Stop Words Removal:**"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "fMZuPQPy9ewL"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "  Stop words are common words that add little meaning to text and are often removed in preprocessing.\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "ou-Ga__a9lf9"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import nltk\n",
        "nltk.download('punkt')\n",
        "from nltk.tokenize import word_tokenize\n",
        "text = \"Natural Language Processing is fascinating.\"\n",
        "tokens = word_tokenize(text)\n",
        "print(tokens)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
